### === Слайди 4, 6, 8 — Books REST API v1 ===
### Усі захищені endpoints вимагають JWT — спочатку виконай 03-auth.http

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@jwt = PASTE_JWT_HERE

### GET список (Слайд 6: GET, кешування через Cache-Control, Deprecation header)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/books
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### GET одна книга
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/books/1
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### POST створити (Слайд 6: 201 Created + Location header)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/books
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Spring in Action",
  "author": "Craig Walls",
  "isbn": "9781617297571",
  "priceUah": 1100
}

### PUT оновити (повне оновлення)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/books/1
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Kotlin in Action (2nd ed.)",
  "author": "Dmitry Jemerov",
  "isbn": "9781617293290",
  "priceUah": 950
}

### DELETE видалити (Слайд 10: 204 No Content)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/books/3
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### Слайд 10 — Валідаційна помилка (400 + структуроване тіло)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/books
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "",
  "author": "Test",
  "isbn": "bad",
  "priceUah": -10
}

### Слайд 10 — 404 Not Found
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/books/9999
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}
